description:
Password manager with goals to be Secure, Simple to use, Portable, Extensible rust-keylock is a password manager and its goals are to be:
  • Secure
  • Simple to use
  • Portable
  • Extensible
rust-keylock-android is an Android app that provides access to

rust-keylock-lib

. The minimum supported Android API level is 30.

Warning:

The project has not yet received any formal / official security reviews. Use it at your own risk.
